<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/964142-is-this-book-written-in-an-alternative">Is this book written in an alternative style of English? I have no idea what&#39;s happening.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_964142'><a id="like_count_community_question_964142" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/964142?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">9 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F2794.The_Crying_of_Lot_49">like</a></span>

