<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1092537-what-other-authors-are-like-this-i-love">What other authors are like this? I love the writing style. I&#39;ve read: David Foster Wallace; Raymond Carver, loved both. I own Maxon &amp; Dixon but the language and style (and size) got the best of me...wonder if it&#39;s worth trying again...</a>
